description:
    These are exmples originally written for the Gtk2Hs suite of libraries
    ported to use haskell-gi instead.
category: Graphics
author: Axel Simon, Duncan Coutts and many others
tested-with: GHC ==7.0.4 GHC ==7.2.2 GHC ==7.4.1
